---
title: Smart Golden Shrimp and Coconut Sauce with Veggies and Couscous
description: As golden and bright as it is delicious and filling, tonight's dinner is also guilt-free! We're serving it with less conventional--but delicious--veggie-studded couscous to help soak up all of that tasty coconut broth.

